    "causal_summary": "The sk-prompt benchmark surface contains underscore-separated authored result directories such as live_final, router_final, and router_mode_a, plus generated raw-run filenames with double underscores. This phase renames authored benchmark paths, updates path references, and records generated/frozen output dispositions without changing benchmark payload keys, fixtures, profiles, or scores.",
